# planning 
UniWell health tracker that supports SDG3: Good Health and Well-Being.

## Mission
Our mission is to empower students to take control of their health by providing a simple, accessible, and reliable application.
The student health tracker will help users log daily health and receive personalized reminders, and access emergency support when needed. By fostering healthier rountines and ensuring timely medical assistance, 
our solution contributes to SDG3:Good Health and Well-Being, promoting a safer and more supportive university enviroment.

### Vision
Our vision is to create a application that empowers students to monitor their health, receive reminders on time, and access emergency supports. By promoting proactive health management, 
the app contributes to SDG3: Good Health and Well-Being, makes sure that students can maintain healthier lifesytles and receive assisstance when needed.

#### User stories(Backlog)
Authentication
As a student, I want to log in with my email address and password so that i can securely access my personal health records.

Health record
As a student, I wan to record my water intake, sleep hours, meals and execrise so that i can track my daily health habits.

Data visualization
As a student, I want to be able to see clearly on the dashboard how much water i've drunk and how long i.ve slept today, so i know how far i am from daily goals.

Smart reminder
As a student, I want to receive reminders if i forgot to record data so i dont break my health tracking plan.

Admin functions
As a admin, I want to manage user accounts so that the system can run properly.

